<i>adverb</i>: 선뜻 [선뜯], 기꺼이 [기꺼이] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>선뜻 [선뜯]</dt><br>
<dd>readily; gladly; willingly</dd><br>
<dd>아무 망설임이나 어려움 없이 쉽게.</dd><br>
<dd>Promptly without hesitation or difficulties.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>기꺼이 [기꺼이]</dt><br>
<dd>willingly; gladly</dd><br>
<dd>기쁜 마음으로.</dd><br>
<dd>With pleasure.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>